                       "  3.  Every drum hit is mapped to the correct Paradiddle note value\n"
                       "  4.  Any drum sounds that don't exist in Paradiddle are automatically\n"
                       "      remapped to the nearest equivalent (e.g. hand clap → snare,\n"
