                       "  ✓  Note counts per drum — make sure kick, snare, hi-hat etc. look right\n"
                       "  ℹ  Remapped notes — notes that were auto-converted to a nearby drum sound.\n"
                       "      Review these to make sure the substitution makes sense for your song.\n"
                       "  ⚠  Dropped notes — notes with no Paradiddle equivalent. If something\n"
