              "  - Neural Stem Isolation actually works now. Since v4.4.4\n"
              "    the new \"Neural Stem Isolation\" toggle in Audio → MIDI\n"
              "    Settings was silently failing right at the start of\n"
              "    every conversion — the splitter never ran, and ParaKit\n"
