              "  - MIDI Editor: 'Snap to grid' toggle is now visible again. The\n"
              "    checkbox at the top of the Display Options box was being drawn\n"
              "    with invisible text by the dark theme (you could click where it\n"
              "    should have been, but the label and checkbox didn't render).\n"
              "    Fixed by switching the widget to the same explicit dark-theme\n"
              "    style used by Reclassify mode just below it.\n"
              "  - Scrollbar styling: the MIDI Editor's horizontal scrollbar is\n"
              "    now the same dark + purple color as the rest of the app's\n"
